prompt.text: 1. What is the name of the interviewer?
What is the name of the interviewer?
2. Choose field site
Specify other site
3. Collect the GPS coordinates

hint.text: You must take a GPS recording. This may take >5 minutes.

prompt.text: Enter GPS coordinates manually (if necessary)
4. If you did not take GPS, please explain why not

hint.text: Skip if GPS was taken

prompt.text: If you did not take GPS, please explain why not (other)
5. GPS ID (location type)
6. In your (the interviewer's) knowledge, has anyone in this household had Lassa fever?

hint.text: To be answered by interviewer

prompt.text: 7. I'd like to ask you questions in order to help us conduct research in hopes to improve healthcare for Lassa fever. Redeemer University, the University of Cambridge, and our partners may have access to this information, including your current location. .  Note that you may withdraw your permission at any time and ask for your data to be erased. Choosing to not participate will in no way affect the care and treatment you will receive. Are you happy to participate?
8. Registration date

hint.text: Today's date

prompt.text: 9. What is the name of the individual consenting to registering the household?
10. Who is the head of this household?

hint.text: This might not be the person you are interviewing

prompt.text: What is their first name?
What is their other name?
What is their surname?
11. Name of Community
Name of Community (Other)
12. Village/City name
Village/City name (Other)
13. Town
14. Address

hint.text: Enter if there is a formal address; otherwise skip

prompt.text: 15. LGA
16. How many people live in this household?

hint.text: In total, including you. (Note: only people who regularly eat from the same pot count as being part of one household)

prompt.text: 16. Is this house located on or beside a farm?
17. What is grown on the farm?
18. Specify what is grown
18. How many minutes away is the closest farm (walking)?
22. Have you or anyone in your household ever been diagnosed with Lassa?

hint.text: Only select Yes if the person was diagnosed PCR positive for Lassa

prompt.text: 23. When was the most recent case of Lassa fever diagnosed in this household?

hint.text: Only answer if the person was diagnosed PCR positive for Lassa

prompt.text: 24. Has anyone died from Lassa fever in this household?

hint.text: Only answer if the person was diagnosed PCR positive for Lassa

hint.text: Do not include rare events, such as land sale
